# Virtual Layer Topology

Proxmox VM Host:
- VM1: Windows Server 2019/2022 (AD Domain Controller)
- VM2: Ubuntu Server (Utility & SIEM testing)
- VM3: pfSense (Firewall)

VLANs:
- VLAN 10: Lab VMs
- VLAN 20: Management / Firewall
- VLAN 30: DNS / IoT (Pi-hole on Raspberry Pi)

External Devices:
- Gaming PC → VLAN 20 → Remote VM management
- Odyssey G9 Monitor connected to Gaming PC
- TP-Link EAP610 → Provides LAN/WAN connectivity
